ddl:
CREATE TABLE `bigquery-public-data.sdoh_snap_enrollment.snap_enrollment`
(
  GeoDesc STRING OPTIONS(description="Substate/Region with Program"),
  SNAP_PA_Participation_Persons INT64 OPTIONS(description="SNAP All Persons Public Assistance Participation"),
  SNAP_NPA_Participation_Persons INT64 OPTIONS(description="SNAP All Persons Non-Public Assistance Participation"),
  SNAP_All_Participation_Persons INT64 OPTIONS(description="Calc: SNAP Total PA and Non-PA People"),
  SNAP_PA_Participation_Households INT64 OPTIONS(description="SNAP All Households Public Assistance Participation"),
  SNAP_NPA_Participation_Households INT64 OPTIONS(description="SNAP All Households Non-Public Assistance Participation"),
  SNAP_All_Participation_Households INT64 OPTIONS(description="Calc: SNAP Total PA and Non-PA Households"),
  SNAP_All_Issuance INT64 OPTIONS(description="SNAP All Total Actual PA & Non-PA Issuance"),
  Date DATE OPTIONS(description="Data of Enrollment Data"),
  FIPS STRING OPTIONS(description="County FIPS Designation"),
  SubCounty STRING OPTIONS(description="SubCounty Assigned Number"),
  Program STRING OPTIONS(description="Program Abbreviation")
)
OPTIONS(
  labels=[("freebqcovid", "")]
);
